        <updateDate>2007-02-23T22:07:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Congressional Whistleblower Protection Act of 2007 - Amends the Congressional Accountability Act of 1995 to apply whistleblower rights and protections to legislative branch employees, including those of the Government Accountability Office or the Library of Congress.</p> <p>Prescribes for violation of this Act the same remedy as would be appropriate if awarded with respect to a prohibited federal personnel practice in the executive branch.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
